<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="и®ӯз»ғзҪ‘з»ң">и®ӯз»ғзҪ‘з»ң
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/3-02-classification/#и®ӯз»ғзҪ‘з»ң" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>и®ӯз»ғзҡ„жӯҘйӘӨеҫҲз®ҖеҚ•, еҰӮдёӢ:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># optimizer жҳҜи®ӯз»ғзҡ„е·Ҙе…·
</span><span class="n">optimizer</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">optim</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SGD</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">net</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">(),</span> <span class="n">lr</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.02</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># дј е…Ҙ net зҡ„жүҖжңүеҸӮж•°, еӯҰд№ зҺҮ
# з®—иҜҜе·®зҡ„ж—¶еҖҷ, жіЁж„Ҹзңҹе®һеҖј!дёҚжҳҜ! one-hot еҪўејҸзҡ„, иҖҢжҳҜ1D Tensor, (batch,)
# дҪҶжҳҜйў„жөӢеҖјжҳҜ2D tensor (batch, n_classes)
</span><span class="n">loss_func</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">CrossEntropyLoss</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">out</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">net</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>     <span class="c1"># е–Ӯз»ҷ net и®ӯз»ғж•°жҚ® x, иҫ“еҮәеҲҶжһҗеҖј
</span>
    <span class="n">loss</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">loss_func</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="p">)</span>     <span class="c1"># и®Ўз®—дёӨиҖ…зҡ„иҜҜе·®
</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zero_grad</span><span class="p">()</span>   <span class="c1"># жё…з©әдёҠдёҖжӯҘзҡ„ж®ӢдҪҷжӣҙж–°еҸӮж•°еҖј
</span>    <span class="n">loss</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">backward</span><span class="p">()</span>         <span class="c1"># иҜҜе·®еҸҚеҗ‘дј ж’ӯ, и®Ўз®—еҸӮж•°жӣҙж–°еҖј
</span>    <span class="n">optimizer</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>        <span class="c1"># е°ҶеҸӮж•°жӣҙж–°еҖјж–ҪеҠ еҲ° net зҡ„ parameters дёҠ
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҸҜи§ҶеҢ–и®ӯз»ғиҝҮзЁӢ">еҸҜи§ҶеҢ–и®ӯз»ғиҝҮзЁӢ
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/3-02-classification/#еҸҜи§ҶеҢ–и®ӯз»ғиҝҮзЁӢ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>дёәдәҶеҸҜи§ҶеҢ–ж•ҙдёӘи®ӯз»ғзҡ„иҝҮзЁӢ, жӣҙеҘҪзҡ„зҗҶи§ЈжҳҜеҰӮдҪ•и®ӯз»ғ, жҲ‘д»¬еҰӮдёӢж“ҚдҪң:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">matplotlib.pyplot</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">plt</span>

<span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ion</span><span class="p">()</span>   <span class="c1"># з”»еӣҫ
</span><span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">show</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="o">...</span>
    <span class="n">loss</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">backward</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>

    <span class="c1"># жҺҘзқҖдёҠйқўжқҘ
</span>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cla</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="c1"># иҝҮдәҶдёҖйҒ“ softmax зҡ„жҝҖеҠұеҮҪж•°еҗҺзҡ„жңҖеӨ§жҰӮзҺҮжүҚжҳҜйў„жөӢеҖј
</span>        <span class="n">prediction</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="nb">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">F</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">softmax</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="n">pred_y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">prediction</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">numpy</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">squeeze</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">target_y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">numpy</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">scatter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">numpy</span><span class="p">()[:,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">numpy</span><span class="p">()[:,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">pred_y</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">lw</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">cmap</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">'RdYlGn'</span><span class="p">)</span>
